sentences.english: Researching progress on the synthesis methodology of fluoropyridazines is described.
sentences.chinese: 敘述了氟代噠嗪化合物合成方法學研究進展。

sentences.english: The recent progress in research on pyridazinone derivatives was summarized in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 簡要綜述噠嗪酮類化合物近年來的藥用研究進展。

sentences.english: The fungicidal activities of pyridazine derivatives reported in recent years were reviewed according to different chemical structures.
sentences.chinese: 按照結構進行分類，對近年來噠嗪類衍。
